statements: SELECT lead_name, lead_score, lead_id FROM LeadScoringModels;
SELECT * FROM LeadScoringModels;
SELECT lead_name FROM LeadScoringModels ORDER BY lead_name DESC;
SELECT lead_id, lead_name FROM LeadScoringModels WHERE lead_score > 50;
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM LeadScoringModels;
SELECT lead_id, lead_name, lead_score FROM LeadScoringModels WHERE lead_score > 80 ORDER BY lead_name DESC
SELECT * FROM LeadScoringModels WHERE lead_score < 50 ORDER BY lead_id ASC
SELECT lead_name, lead_score FROM LeadScoringModels WHERE lead_name LIKE 'A%' OR lead_name LIKE '%Z' ORDER BY lead_score DESC
SELECT DISTINCT lead_score FROM LeadScoringModels ORDER BY lead_score ASC LIMIT 3
SELECT AVG(lead_score) AS average_score FROM LeadScoringModels WHERE lead_score < 100 GROUP BY lead_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
SELECT * FROM lead_scores;
SELECT lead_id, lead_name FROM lead_scores WHERE lead_score > 80;
SELECT lead_name, lead_score FROM lead_scores ORDER BY lead_score DESC;
SELECT * FROM lead_history WHERE lead_status = 'Qualified' ORDER BY last_interaction DESC;
SELECT lead_id, lead_status, last_interaction FROM lead_history WHERE last_interaction > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM lead_scores WHERE lead_score > 80 ORDER BY lead_name ASC;
SELECT lead_name, lead_score FROM lead_scores WHERE lead_score < 50 ORDER BY lead_score DESC;
SELECT lead_name, lead_status FROM lead_scores JOIN lead_history ON lead_scores.lead_id = lead_history.lead_id WHERE lead_history.last_interaction > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY lead_name;

SELECT lead_name, COUNT(lead_history.history_id) AS interaction_count FROM lead_scores LEFT JOIN lead_history ON lead_scores.lead_id = lead_history.lead_id GROUP BY lead_scores.lead_id ORDER BY interaction_count DESC;

SELECT lead_name, lead_status, last_interaction FROM lead_scores JOIN lead_history ON lead_scores.lead_id = lead_history.lead_id WHERE lead_scores.lead_score > 60 AND lead_history.lead_status = 'active' ORDER BY last_interaction DESC;
SELECT * FROM lead_scores;
SELECT lead_id, lead_name FROM lead_scores WHERE lead_score > 50;
SELECT lead_name, lead_score FROM lead_scores ORDER BY lead_score DESC;
SELECT lead_id, interaction_type, interaction_date FROM lead_interaction WHERE interaction_type = 'Email';
SELECT lead_id, sales_rep, sales_date, deal_value FROM sales_efforts WHERE deal_value > 10000 ORDER BY sales_date ASC;
SELECT lead_id, lead_name, lead_score FROM lead_scores ORDER BY lead_name DESC, lead_id ASC;
SELECT interaction_id, lead_id, interaction_type, interaction_date FROM lead_interaction WHERE interaction_type='Email' ORDER BY interaction_date DESC;
SELECT lead_id, lead_name, SUM(lead_score) as total_score FROM lead_scores GROUP BY lead_id, lead_name HAVING total_score > 100 ORDER BY total_score DESC;
SELECT sales_rep, COUNT(lead_id) as total_leads, AVG(deal_value) as avg_deal_value FROM sales_efforts GROUP BY sales_rep HAVING total_leads > 5 ORDER BY avg_deal_value DESC;

SELECT lead_name, interaction_type, interaction_date, deal_value FROM lead_scores JOIN lead_interaction ON lead_scores.lead_id = lead_interaction.lead_id JOIN sales_efforts ON lead_scores.lead_id = sales_efforts.lead_id WHERE deal_value > 500 ORDER BY interaction_date ASC, deal_value DESC;
SELECT * FROM leads;
SELECT lead_name, lead_email FROM leads WHERE lead_score > 80;
SELECT lead_name, lead_score FROM leads ORDER BY lead_score DESC;
SELECT * FROM lead_scores WHERE last_updated >= '2022-01-01 00:00:00';
SELECT DISTINCT lead_email FROM leads;
SELECT * FROM leads WHERE lead_score > 80;
SELECT lead_name, lead_email FROM leads WHERE lead_score < 50 ORDER BY lead_name DESC;
SELECT l.lead_name, ls.lead_score, t.team_name FROM leads l JOIN lead_scores ls ON l.lead_id = ls.lead_id JOIN sales_team t ON t.team_id = l.lead_id WHERE ls.lead_score BETWEEN 70 AND 90;
SELECT t.team_name, s.sales_rep_name FROM sales_reps s JOIN sales_team t ON s.team_id = t.team_id ORDER BY t.team_name ASC;
SELECT lead_name, lead_score, last_updated FROM leads l JOIN lead_scores ls ON l.lead_id = ls.lead_id WHERE last_updated > '2021-01-01' ORDER BY lead_score DESC;
SELECT * FROM lead_score;
SELECT lead_id, lead_name, lead_score FROM lead_score WHERE lead_status = 'Active';
SELECT lead_id, lead_source FROM lead_score ORDER BY lead_id DESC;
SELECT lead_id, interaction_type, interaction_date FROM lead_interaction WHERE interaction_type = 'Email';
SELECT lead_id, email, phone_number, address FROM lead_contact_info WHERE lead_id = 100;

SELECT lead_name, lead_status FROM lead_score ORDER BY lead_status ASC;
SELECT lead_id, interaction_date, interaction_notes FROM lead_interaction WHERE interaction_type = 'Meeting';
SELECT lead_id, email, phone_number FROM lead_contact_info WHERE email LIKE '%@gmail.com';
